+### Ktlint suppression
+
+Detects the usage of the deprecated `ktlint-disable` and `ktlint-enable` directives in comments. These directives are deprecated and should be replaced with `@Suppress` annotations.
+
+=== "[:material-heart:](#) Ktlint"
+
+    ```kotlin
+    @Suppress("ktlint:standard:no-wildcard-imports")
+    import foo.*
+    
+    @Suppress("ktlint")
+    val foo = "foo"
+    ```
+=== "[:material-heart-off-outline:](#) Disallowed (deprecated)"
+
+    ```kotlin
+    import foo.* // ktlint-disable standard:no-wildcard-imports
+    
+    /* ktlint-disable */
+    val foo = "foo"
+    /* ktlint-enable */
+    ```
+
+!!! warning
+    This rule cannot be suppressed. It will always report violations for deprecated directives.
+
+Rule id: `ktlint-suppression` (`standard` rule set)
+
 ### Keyword spacing
 
 Consistent spacing around keywords.
